{"type":"message","id":"d203527e","parentId":"fe238558","timestamp":"2026-03-10T07:15:05.208Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to read the configuration file to understand what stock monitoring tasks to execute.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d8fb083c17384efeaf42f836","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data-cron-config.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773126900082}}
{"type":"message","id":"cae15c20","parentId":"d203527e","timestamp":"2026-03-10T07:15:05.212Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d8fb083c17384efeaf42f836","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 实时数据获取操作\n\n**重要提示**\n- 你的工作路径：~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock\n- 自定义文件路径：~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock\n- 你独享的skill存放位置：~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/skills\n- 以下描述中没有具体位置的文件都是自定义文件，存放在自定义路径下，\n  如'realtime-data.txt'实际路径为：~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt；\n- 指定了具体路径的文件，按照指定路径读取，如：~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/TOOLS.md；\n- 如果你需要新建文件，统一存放在自定义路径下；\n- 如果存在可用脚本，优先复用，不满足当前场景时才允许创建新脚本。\n- 执行到不存在的文件时，请严格检查是否时按照上述要求执行的。\n\n### 操作流程\n\n1、使用tushare-data skill，获取数据判断今日是否收盘或休市，未收盘或休市，则进行下一步；否则，结束本次任务；\n2、如果realtime-data.txt里的内容不为空，则清空后进行下一步；否则直接进行下一步；\n3、阅读~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/TOOLS.md内的skill使用说明，严格按照要求使用skill；\n4、使用tushare-data skill，按照get-data-template.md内的格式要求获取自选股的实时日线数据，保存在realtime-data.txt里；\n5、按照alert-rules.md中的预警规则和以下条件过滤获取到的实时数据：\n   - 满足预警规则中任意一条条件；\n   - 只返回满足预警规则的数据；\n6、如果存在满足条件的数据，则进行下一步；否则，结束本次任务。\n7、读取receiver-list.txt接受者用户列表文件，使用命令openclaw message broadcast --channel feishu --account stock --targets <user_id1> --targets <user_id2>... --message <xxx>，\n   将预警数据通过飞书(feishu)渠道推送给列表文件中的用户；\n   - --targets <user_id> 参数可重复\n8、推送数据格式严格按照alert-template.md的内容要求。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773126905210}}
{"type":"message","id":"2399704d","parentId":"cae15c20","timestamp":"2026-03-10T07:15:09.577Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to read the referenced configuration files (TOOLS.md, get-data-template.md, alert-rules.md, receiver-list.txt, alert-template.md) to understand the skill usage, data format, alert rules, recipients, and message template before executing the monitoring task.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_dde3ce05a82d4193b37b7a73","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/TOOLS.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_dd9f12495c704076bfd32adc","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/get-data-template.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c610c170559e4f548f615b68","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-rules.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_64e0653c680849d7b3e15e1a","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/receiver-list.txt"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f0abafd61e5342ca89e0a604","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-template.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773126905212}}
{"type":"message","id":"6eb89482","parentId":"2399704d","timestamp":"2026-03-10T07:15:09.580Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_dde3ce05a82d4193b37b7a73","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# TOOLS.md - Local Notes\n\n## 你的工作区~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock\n- 所有的技能操作都只能在这个工作区下进行\n- 包括创建文件、删除文件、修改文件\n- 如果有skill要求你在~/下操作，统一重定向到~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock\n\n## 固定文件位置\n- 我的自选股全部维护在~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/watchlist.txt下，相关操作统一在此维护\n- 预警规则维护在~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-rules.md，相关操作统一在此文件中维护\n\n\n## 常用技能速查\n\n### 股票分析\n- 优先使用tushare-data skill获取数据,tushare_token已经配置在环境变量里，可通过env获取\n- 实时数据定义：最近1-2分钟内的数据\n- 进行涨跌分析时，注意要获取实时数据,参考https://tushare.pro/document/2?doc_id=15，学习如何使用实时数据接口\n- 以下是获取实时数据的一系列接口文档，严格参考接口文档获取数据：\n -- 实时分钟：https://tushare.pro/document/2?doc_id=374\n -- 实时日线: https://tushare.pro/document/2?doc_id=372,用于涨跌预警的核心接口\n -- 每个可调用的接口都优先使用可批量获取数据的参数，如：ts_code字段支持单个和多个（600000.SH 或者 600000.SH,000001.SZ），优先使用多个参数的调用方式，防止限流\n- 数据要用不同接口返回的数据进行校对，确保准确性和时效性\n\n## 禁忌\n- 非必要不自行定义脚本\n- 不允许在工作空间外操作数据\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773126909579}}
{"type":"message","id":"4b4cb000","parentId":"6eb89482","timestamp":"2026-03-10T07:15:09.583Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_dd9f12495c704076bfd32adc","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 数据获取模板\n\n按照以下格式获取【我的自选股票】的最新行情数据：\n\n【必选字段】\n1. 代码 - 6 位数字/字母组合\n2. 名称 - 中文全称\n3. 当前股价 (close) - ¥XX.XX 元\n4. 涨跌幅 - +X.XX% / -X.XX%\n5. 涨跌额 - ¥XX.XX 元\n5. 时间点 - YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS\n\n【可选字段 - 根据需求添加】\n- 最新价（close）同：当前股价\n- 昨收价(pre_close)\n- 今开价(open)\n- 最高价\n- 最低价\n- 成交量\n- 成交额\n- 市盈率\n- 总市值\n- 换手率\n\n【计算规则】\n- 涨跌额 = 当前股价 - 昨收价\n- 涨跌额 = (当前股价 - 昨收价) / 昨收价\n\n【数据源要求】\n- 优先级：Tushare Pro > 东方财富 > 同花顺\n- 实时性：优先使用盘口最新报价\n- 准确性：需交叉验证（建议用网页端确认）\n\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773126909582}}
{"type":"message","id":"4af411e9","parentId":"4b4cb000","timestamp":"2026-03-10T07:15:09.587Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_c610c170559e4f548f615b68","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 预警规则\n\n### 通用规则\n1、下跌 > 3% → 触发\n2、上涨 > 5% → 触发\n\n### 个股专属规则\n**中国石油 (601857.SH)**:\n- 🟢 涨幅 > 2% → 触发预警\n- 🔴 跌幅 > 1% → 触发预警\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773126909586}}
{"type":"message","id":"2c75627d","parentId":"4af411e9","timestamp":"2026-03-10T07:15:09.590Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_64e0653c680849d7b3e15e1a","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\nou_0737da20bef21e4dff04d2b83f927208\nou_144623d3a3b4a119305355db7813bb31\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773126909589}}
{"type":"message","id":"5dc62301","parentId":"2c75627d","timestamp":"2026-03-10T07:15:09.593Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f0abafd61e5342ca89e0a604","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 预警数据输出模版\n\n**注意**：数据来源必须标明\n\n【输出格式】\n表格形式，每页输出10条数据,按涨跌幅排序，高亮异常波动\n\n示例：\n| 代码 | 名称 | 当前价 | 涨跌幅 | 涨跌额| 时间 |\n|------|------|--------|--------|-------|------|\n| XXXX | XXXX | ¥XX.XX | +X.XX% |￥XXXX |hh:mm |\n\n⚙️ 预警规则\n• 📉 下跌 > x% → 触发\n• 📈 上涨 > x% → 触发\n\n【数据来源】\n数据来源：xxx\n更新时间：yyyy-MM-dd hh:mm\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773126909592}}
